OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FAn internet blackout in Iran, imposed
OL,7,Fon the first day of the war, has
OL,8,Fentered its tenth week. Hidden from
OL,9,Fthe outside world, the shutdown has
OL,10,Fbecome a powerful tool of control for
OL,11,Fthe regime. Shielded from scrutiny,
OL,12,Fharassment, arrests and even
OL,13,Fexecutions of those who speak out
OL,14,Fremain a constant threat.
OL,16,FOur filmmaker and his friends have
OL,17,Frisked their lives to document daily
OL,18,Flife inside a country largely cut off
OL,19,Ffrom view since February 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
