OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FAt first glance, everything looks
OL,7,Fnormal, but while the bombs have
OL,8,Fstopped falling, Iranians face an
OL,9,Funcertain future.
OL,11,FPrices have risen by more than 70%,
OL,12,Fand millions have lost their jobs. Up
OL,13,Fto 4.1 million people face poverty due
OL,14,Fto the conflict, according to the UN
OL,15,FDevelopment Programme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FHossein moved to Tehran to pursue a
OL,7,Fcareer in films, an industry tightly
OL,8,Fcensored by the regime and starved of
OL,9,Ffunding. Now, war has completely
OL,10,Freshaped his life. Instead of making
OL,11,Ffilms, Hossein is driving a taxi to
OL,12,Fsurvive.
OL,14,FOur filmmaker records him carefully
OL,15,Finside the car, constantly checking
OL,16,Fthey are not being followed, wary of
OL,17,Fattracting the attention of the
OL,18,Fsecurity services, well aware of the
OL,19,Frisks they are taking talking to
OL,20,Fforeign media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,F"Just being alive is something,"
OL,7,FHossein says.
OL,9,FTo pass the time, he and his friends
OL,10,Fvisit the bomb sites and guess how
OL,11,Flarge the explosions were.
OL,13,F"You don't know whether to be happy or
OL,14,Fsad, to say 'bravo, look, they hit
OL,15,Fthis place'."
OL,17,F"I stayed at home for 40 days to see
OL,18,Fwhat the result of the bombs would be,
OL,19,Fwill it change our lives? Not only did
OL,20,Fit fail in bringing us anything, but
OL,21,Fwe also lost what we had - our jobs."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FNegar is also out of work. She never
OL,7,Fsupported the war and now she's
OL,8,Fstruggling with the cost of food,
OL,9,Fwhich is up 30% on last week alone.
OL,11,F"The situation with people's
OL,12,Flivelihoods is at a crisis point. The
OL,13,Fprivate sector is at a standstill, so
OL,14,Fwe can't find funds for our projects.
OL,15,FBut the security situation is a big
OL,16,Fpart of it too. You can't travel to
OL,17,Fparts of the country which are far or
OL,18,Fnear the border. They want to question
OL,19,Fyou all the time."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
