PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FWhile the war with the US and Israel
OL,7,Fhas paused, another kind of conflict
OL,8,Fcontinues inside the country.
OL,10,FSince the war began, the Basij militia
OL,11,Fhas set up checkpoints across the
OL,12,Fcity, routinely arresting those they
OL,13,Fdeem hostile to the regime.
OL,15,F"The security checks were really bad
OL,16,Fduring the war, they would stop every
OL,17,Fcar, check under your seat, your boot,
OL,18,Fwhat have you got in your bag, your
OL,19,Fdashboard, what have you got on your
OL,20,Fphone?" Hossein says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,F"They've given us so much fear that
OL,7,Fyou're scared of everything. You're
OL,8,Fscared of your own phone! One of my
OL,9,Fpassengers was telling me how every
OL,10,Fmorning he deletes everything on his
OL,11,Fphone before he goes to work, even
OL,12,Fthough he has nothing on it!"
OL,14,FWhile many oppose the theocratic
OL,15,Fregime that has ruled since the
OL,16,Frevolution in 1979, millions of
OL,17,FIranians still support the country's
OL,18,Fleaders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
