PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FPro-government supporters hold regular
OL,7,Frallies in the streets, where they
OL,8,Fwave flags, chant slogans and hold
OL,9,Fimages of former Supreme Leader, Ali
OL,10,FKhamenei or his successor, his son,
OL,11,FMojtaba.
OL,13,FHossein tells us the nights are
OL,14,Fparticularly difficult. "They
OL,15,F(government supporters) spill out into
OL,16,Fthe streets waving their flags, they
OL,17,Fcut off the streets as if it belongs
OL,18,Fto them. You beep all you can and try
OL,19,Fto tell them you need to get
OL,20,Fsomewhere...nothing."
OL,26,@wD@ApmwD@Wpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
