CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FReza was among those who protested
OL,7,Fagainst the regime in January, which
OL,8,Fled to a crackdown that left thousands
OL,9,Fdead.
OL,11,F"We didn't know what we were facing.
OL,12,FThe number of people in the streets in
OL,13,Fthe areas we were in was unbelievable.
OL,14,FWe thought it could be over, it would
OL,15,Fbe the end of the story, but then bad
OL,16,Fthings started to happen, the internet
OL,17,Fand phone lines were cut, and then we
OL,18,Fslowly realised that the crackdown was
OL,19,Fgoing to be serious.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,F"The circle of people who were killed
OL,7,Fwas getting closer and closer to us,
OL,8,Fand just like in Covid, when that
OL,9,Fcircle gets closer and closer to you,
OL,10,Fyou realise that a lot of people have
OL,11,Fbeen killed."
OL,13,FLike many Iranians who protested, Reza
OL,14,Fthought the war would bring change,
OL,15,Fbut now he's wondering if they're
OL,16,Fworse off than before.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,F"Most people wanted this war because
OL,7,Fthey felt they couldn't stand up to
OL,8,Fthe strength of the regime and they
OL,9,Fthought the US and Israel could stand
OL,10,Fup to them.
OL,12,F"People feel that instead of weakening
OL,13,Fthe regime, this war has just done
OL,14,Fdamage to people and they haven't seen
OL,15,Fthe positive change they wanted from
OL,16,Fthe war."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778105470
OL,3,CSecret filming in Iran during
OL,4,Cceasefire reveals fear and frustration
OL,6,FFor Hossein, his worldview has changed
OL,7,Ftoo. "I've gone from someone who
OL,8,Fthought 'please let there be a war so
OL,9,Fthere can be change so we can breathe'
OL,10,Fto thinking, 'ok, stay, but let me
OL,11,Fplease have my job so I can earn money
OL,12,Fto live'. Bombs were dropped, but what
OL,13,Fgood did it do for me, who loves films
OL,14,Fand art?"
